{
  "stem": "10825.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 25.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we couldn't get out because even the Jewish communists didn't let us out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because we were very-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] valuable to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we went to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We came to the-- to the-- to the bureau of-- to the travel-- not travel bureau, but the-- to the government, to ask what we can do.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "With bayonets, they said-- they-- they-- they pushed us away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we found out that one general, he was the one who could say yes or no about immigration.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we found a way to come to find him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we have an audience with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he said, Mr. and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Fershko, you are such wonderful artists.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'll give you a Steinway piano, what you deserve.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to live in the capital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we should enjoy your artistry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he finished I said, General, every stone in Warsaw, is soaked in Jewish blood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We can't live, anymore, in-- in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We live in Szczecin because it also-- it was a broken city, a demolished city after the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we didn't know Szczecin before the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we knew Warsaw before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you want, really, to help us, help us to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, Israel?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A country that's just born and starts from anew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I say, Israel starts from anew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have to start from anew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next day, all the doors that were closed, were open.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was please.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Please, in two hours we had the visa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I'm talking all about us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now I want to tell you, that in Szczecin, we met a wonderful lady, who went through a lot in her life during the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Her name was Elsa Frank.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was the only daughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
